      '<p><span><span style="color: #003163;">Simrad Precision-9 Compass</span></span></p>\n<p>The Precision-9 Compass supplies accurate heading and rate-of-turn information to<span> </span><a href="https://www.echomasterdirect.co.uk/Autopilot/Autopilot_Packages/SIMRAD_A2004_Autopilot_Pack__excludes_heading_sensor_" target="_blank">Simrad autopilot</a>,<span> </span><a href="https://www.echomasterdirect.co.uk/Radar" target="_blank">radar</a><span> </span>and<span> </span><a href="https://www.echomasterdirect.co.uk/Chartplotters/Multifunction_Displays&amp;min=&amp;max=&amp;filter=1" target="_blank">navigation systems</a><span> </span>over an NMEA 2000® connection.</p>\n<p>With an internal array of solid-state sensors constantly measuring motion and orientation on nine axes, the Precision-9 also provides pitch and roll data to compatible equipment.</p>\n<p>An easily adjustable mounting bracket and single-cable connection allow simple installation aboard any vessel, including up-mast mounting suitable for steel hulls.</p>\n<p><b>Note;<span> </span></b>If you do not have an existing NMEA2000 network, NMEA2000 Starter Kit 000-0124-69 must also be purchased.</p>\n<p><span><span style="color: #003163;">Key Features</span></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Heading, Rate Of Turn (ROT), pitch and roll output over NMEA 2000®</li>\n<li>Accurate and reliable solid-state sensor technology</li>\n<li>Heading accuracy of ±2° after calibration</li>\n<li>Easily adjustable mounting bracket allows bulkhead or up-mast installation</li>\n<li>IPX7 waterproof for external up-mast mounting on steel hulled vessels</li>\n<li>Simple installation with a single NMEA 2000® connection</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style="color: #003163;"><span>In the Box</span></span></p>\n<p>Simrad Precision-9 Compass, mounting bracket, 4.5m NMEA2000 cable &amp; NMEA2000 T-connector.</p>',
